OL,3,CNavy veteran remembers being told to
OL,4,C'save who you can' during Boscastle
OL,5,CFloods
OL,7,FA Royal Navy veteran has recalled the
OL,8,Fhorror of flying over Boscastle, 20
OL,9,Fyears after the village was hit by
OL,10,Fdevastating flash floods.
OL,12,FLt Cdr Martin 'Florry' Ford was one of
OL,13,Fthe first on the scene in his Sea King
OL,14,Fhelicopter of 771 Naval Air Squadron,
OL,15,Fwhen flash flood devastated North
OL,16,FCornwall on 16 August 2004.
OL,18,FA wall of water surged through
OL,19,FBoscastle with terrifying force,
OL,20,Fdragging cars, trees and debris
OL,21,Fthrough both villages.
