OL,3,CNavy veteran remembers being told to
OL,4,C'save who you can' during Boscastle
OL,5,CFloods
OL,7,FNine aircraft hovered in the skies
OL,8,Fabove, managing to airlift around 120
OL,9,Fpeople to safety, many from damaged
OL,10,Fbuildings and stranded vehicles. They
OL,11,Fensured that no-one was killed.
OL,13,FAmong the three Royal Navy
OL,14,Fhelicopters, three RAF helicopters,
OL,15,Ftwo civilian air ambulances and a
OL,16,Fcoastguard aircraft was Lt Cdr Florry
OL,17,FFord.
