OL,3,CNavy veteran remembers being told to
OL,4,C'save who you can' during Boscastle
OL,5,CFloods
OL,7,F"We were sat outside over the sea, as
OL,8,Fvisibility was terrible, and we were
OL,9,Fhit by a microburst," he said. "The
OL,10,Frain was that heavy it was like a
OL,11,Fwaterfall running off the rotor blades
OL,12,Fall around us.
OL,14,F"We were having to bail out the
OL,15,Faircraft with our helmets. It was that
OL,16,Fserious that I remember Pete McLelland
OL,17,Fsaid to us: 'Look boys, remind
OL,18,Fyourselves of the exits'."
