OL,3,CNavy veteran remembers being told to
OL,4,C'save who you can' during Boscastle
OL,5,CFloods
OL,7,F"It was probably one of the last
OL,8,Fcommunications I had from one of the
OL,9,FCoastguard saying, 'Save who you can'
OL,10,Fand that just made that's on the back
OL,11,Fof my neck stand up."
OL,13,FIt was a technically difficult mission
OL,14,Fnavigating around so many aircraft in
OL,15,Fsuch a small space, while also
OL,16,Favoiding power cables.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
