OL,3,CNavy veteran remembers being told to
OL,4,C'save who you can' during Boscastle
OL,5,CFloods
OL,7,F"At one point as we were coming into
OL,8,Fland, you could see cows licking
OL,9,Ftrout. The farm had flooded and sadly,
OL,10,Fall of these trout washed into the
OL,11,Ffield with the cows staring at them.
OL,12,FIt was just obscene things which you
OL,13,Fnever see, you hopefully will never
OL,14,Fsee again."
OL,16,FNow retired, the former Lt Cdr said he
OL,17,F"cannot believe" there were no
OL,18,Ffatalities and spent the following
OL,19,Fweeks tracking the news expecting to
OL,20,Fhear somebody had been found.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
