OL,3,CNavy veteran remembers being told to
OL,4,C'save who you can' during Boscastle
OL,5,CFloods
OL,7,FToday however, he does not feel
OL,8,Fconfident the UK's search and rescue
OL,9,Foperation is as well equipped for this
OL,10,Fkind of mission.
OL,12,F"At the time there were five out the
OL,13,F20 allocated Search and Rescue assets
OL,14,Finvolved, a total of seven aircraft,
OL,15,Fbut these extra two came from Culdrose
OL,16,Fand St Mawgan."
