OL,3,CNavy veteran remembers being told to
OL,4,C'save who you can' during Boscastle
OL,5,CFloods
OL,7,F"That was 25% of the UK SAR
OL,8,Fcapability. We've now got only ten
OL,9,Fbases, so seven aircraft is 70%. It
OL,10,Fwouldn't leave us a lot of flex for
OL,11,Fanything else that was happening
OL,12,Faround the UK."
